Text: KASIES PHONE NUMBER IN GERMANY FROM THE th TO THE thKASIES PHONE NUMBERS IN GERMANY HER MOBIL NUMBER

Re Sciullo Properties AppraisalIn a message dated Eastern Standard Time Susan NRONcom writes WELCOME BACK Hope you and Dorothy had a pleasant trip to Germany Hope all is well with Kasie I would love to hear all about it WE DID HAVE A GREAT TRIP BUT AS YOU CAN SEE THERE ARE SOME FAMILY PROBLEMS DOROTHY AND I FLEW IN TO PHIL ON THURSDAY AND THEN TOOK A PM FLIGHT TO CONN AND SPENT THURSDAY NIGHT FRIDAY SATURDAY AND SUNDAY BETWEEN THE HOSPITAL AND THE HOME MY FATHER IN LAW IS IN WE LEFT ANT PM SUNDAY NIGHT AND ARRIVED AT THE HOUSE AROUND I SENT YOU A STATUS REPORT ON MY MOTHER IN LAW IT REALLY DOESNT LOOK TO GOOD I AM CATCHING UP TODAY I WILL CALL YOU IN THE NEXT DAY OR SO LEONARD
Re Deposit SUSAN THANK YOU THIS IS FINE I FORGOT ABOUT THE CHECK COMING IN TO THE OFFICE I AM ATTACHING FOR YOUR FILES A COPY OF THE OCTOBER CHECK BOOK REGISTER LEONARD
Re Jackson National Life Quarterly PremiumSUSAN THANK YOU LEONARD
Re Schwab MailingsSusan I DID NOT REQUEST ANY INFO ON ELECTRONIC FUNDS WHEN I DEPOSITED THE FOUR STAR MONEY I ASKED THEM TO SEND YOU FOURSTAR DEPOSIT SLIPS LEONARD

Re Schwab MailingsIn a message dated PM Eastern Standard Time Susan NRONcom writes Do you want me to make a new request I WOULD WAIT A WEEK OR SO AND SEE IF THEY MAIL THEM WHEN I MADE THE DEPOSIT THE FELLOW SAID HE WAS MAILING THE DEPOSITS SLIPS TO YOUR HOUSTON ADDRESSSO I KNOW HE WAS MAKING A REQUEST LEONARD

Re Schwab MailingsSUSAN I AM STILL IN FLORIDA AND I AM USING A LOANER COMPUTER THAT IS VERY TOUCHY I GO TO MOVE THE MOUSE AND THE COMPUTER TAKES OFF IN A SECOND IT SENDS BY ITS SELFSO I JUST SIGNED ON NOW TO CHECK MAIL AND IT MAY HAVE REPLIED AGAIN LEONARD
